videos.headline: No. 21 Hogs' Spencer leads upset of No. 16 Creighton
videos.description: Samara Spencer scores 26 and Saylor Poffenbarger records her third double-double with 16 points and 11 rebounds in Arkansas' 83-75 road win vs. the Bluejays.
